mmas to see if you're worthy of joining \"The Corporation\" to work as a mercenary. Your decisions will impact the story and determine if  you get the job after the grueling interview process. \n\nAre you the right fit for the job? Find out. \n", "short_description": "Time Titans VR is a Singleplayer action shooter that allows the user to manually slow down time to get an advantage in combat. Shoot, punch and slice through enemies while slowing down time to unleash mayhem or dodge counter attacks. "}]}, "developer_name": "Phocore Inc.", "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://www.phocoregames.com/privacy-policy", "developer_terms_of_service_url": "https://www.phocoregames.com/privacy-policy", "publisher_name": "Phocore Inc.", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "https://www.phocoregames.com/", "category": "GAMES", "comfort_rating": "NOT_RATED", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "2743326035925534", "context_category": "GAMES"}, "context_topics": [{"id": "1436351953220286"}, {"id": "459781504968480"}, {"id": "377978390272490"}], "external_subscription_type": "NOT_REQUIRED", "genres": ["ACTION", "SHOOTER", "STRATEGY"], "has_in_app_ads": false, "internet_connection": "NOT_REQUIRED", "play_area": "MOVEMENT", "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": null, "supported_in_app_languages": ["en"], "supported_input_devices": ["OCULUS_TOUCH"], "supported_player_modes": ["STANDING"], "supported_tracking_modes": [], "user_interaction_modes": ["SINGLE_USER"], "id": "1085785358587291"}, "review_messages": ["", "", ""]}]}, "cover_square_image": {"uri": "https://scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39003243_655669045899842_863590056398870483_n.png?stp=dst-png_s360x360&_nc_cat=102&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=xSIZVfhBArsQ7kNvgHQZUbO&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYByAOzNjYTRlwAhy1KzyU4MxzvqQgY-smbInbvgm6VxfQ&oe=6717782B"}, "is_concept": false, "is_test": false, "is_trial_offer_valid": fals